Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
Imports: crayon, testthat, toOrdinal
URL: https://CenterForAssessment.github.io/packageSkeletonForR
BugReports: https://github.com/CenterForAssessment/packageSkeletonForR/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyLoad: Yes
